ActEmergency Management Act
SubjectNo. 124 - (NB) Provincial Emergencies Financial Assistance Order
PrecisPROVINCIAL EMERGENCY FINANCIAL ASSISTANCE ORDER N° 124 - which makes a declaration of federal concern and authorizes the federal government to provide financial assistance to the province of NEW BRUNSWICK with respect to the storm surge which affected the Port Elgin-Baie Verte area of Westmorland County on January 2 and 3, 2010.
